  "title": "Admin Ops Restaurant Manager ( Vegetarian Restaurant)",
  "description": "<p>We’re looking for an organized and reliable Restaurant Manager (Administrative) to support the operations and administrative team of our vegetarian restaurant. ( Part-Time, Full Time) </p><p></p><p>Working Hours: 9:00am – 5:00pm ( weekdays) </p><p>Working Days: 4  days per week</p><p></p><p>Requirements</p><p>* At least 3 years of F&B management or admin experience</p><p>* Basic accounting knowledge (QuickBooks/HR systems a plus)</p><p>* Organised, responsible, and detail-oriented</p><p>* Able to multitask and work independently,</p><p></p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><p>Admin & Accounts Support</p><p>* Handle daily admin work, records, invoices, and simple accounting</p><p>* Manage staff attendance, payroll coordination, and documentation\\<br /></p><p>HR & Staff Coordination</p><p>* Support hiring, scheduling, and basic staff matters</p><p>* Maintain staff records and internal communication<br /></p><p>* Training scheduling  and Onboarding, </p><p></p><p>Operations Support</p><p>* Assist with day-to-day restaurant coordination, check backs.</p><p>* Support events, suppliers, and inventory paperwork</p><p>* Support marketing efforts </p><p>* Training based on established SOPs</p><p>* Sales reporting and performance<br /></p><p>Customer & Business Support</p><p>* Handle enquiries and feedback</p><p>* Assist with reports, promotions, and general coordination</p><p></p><p>Compliance</p><p>* Ensure documents, licenses and basic regulations are in order</p>",
